Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like a cruel angel{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become a legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When a blue wind{\i0}\N{\i1}Knocks on the door to your heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just gaze back at me{\i0}\N{\i1}And smile oh so gently{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So eager for something{\i0}\N{\i1}You touch so softly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those innocent eyes{\i0}\N{\i1}Know nothing of the fate that awaits{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But one day, you will realize{\i0}\N{\i1}That upon your back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have wings{\i0}\N{\i1}You can fly to the faraway future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cruel angel's thesis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you'll take off through a window{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If your overflowing pathos{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leads you to betray your memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then embrace the heavens and shine bright{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.87,0:01:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apoptosis process on three Evas{\i0}\N{\i1}will begin as scheduled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}following Magi system restart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Confirming process.{\i0}\N{\i1}Abbreviate steps 450 to 670.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.97,0:01:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Command Center, approved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very fast, Maya. I'm amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be.\NI learned from the best, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. An A-8 would be faster there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it coming? You done with\Nthe Magis' diagnostic testing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just about. As promised,\Nthey'll be ready before today's testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Ritsuko! Checking over three\Nidentical systems is a tall order!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That coffee is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,ROUTINE DIAGNOSTIC
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All three Magi system units{\i0}\N{\i1}have entered self-diagnostic mode.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Routine diagnostic no. 127{\i0}\N{\i1}shows all systems green.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger. Good work, everyone.{\i0}\N{\i1}Get some rest until the testing starts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All systems green, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother is as healthy as ever,\Nwhile I get older with each passing day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to undress {\i1}again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, you'll be going into{\i0}\N{\i1}a super-clean room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A shower and change of underwear{\i0}\N{\i1}won't cut it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to go through all this\Njust to test some autopilot system?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time isn't the only thing that marches on.{\i0}\N{\i1}So does the Evas' technology.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We constantly need{\i0}\N{\i1}new data to work off of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Here we are,\Nexactly how you want us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeaky clean\Nafter 17 thorough scrubbings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, I need the three of you{\i0}\N{\i1}to remain undressed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go through this room{\i0}\N{\i1}and get into your entry plugs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry, the visual feed is off.{\i0}\N{\i1}We'll respect your privacy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point, and you know it!\NI'm seriously uncomfortable here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The aim of this test is to gauge how well{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}harmonics are picked up from your bodies{\i0}\N{\i1}without the aid of plug suits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asuka, that's an order.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine! But don't you dare peek!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All pilots ready for entry sequence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Start test.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Starting test.{\i0}\N{\i1}Now commencing autopilot recording.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inserting simulation plugs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Connecting systems to imitation bodies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Simulation entry plugs\Nnow under Magi control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at it go!\NThe Magi sure make a big difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a far cry from those first tests\Nthat took a whole week!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Test scheduled to end\Nin approximately three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}How do you feel?{\i0}\N-Something is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not the same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My senses are all messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel my right arm just fine,\Nbut everything else feels hazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rei, mentally picture{\i0}\N{\i1}your right arm moving.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Data collection proceeding smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything seems to be fine.\NReturn the Magi to normal mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An inner conflict...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It really shows the personality\Nof the person who built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NI thought {\i1}you{\i0} built them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know much\Nabout the Magi, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your fault for not talking about\Nyourself as much as I do, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:04:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I only got the system up and running.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who came up with the core theories\Nand {\i1}built{\i0} it was my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-You've verified this?\N-Yes, just to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a part we got in three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is the area\Nthat's deteriorating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Protein wall no. 87, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Under magnification, you can see\Nwhat appears to be stains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be corrosion. There are minute\Ntemperature and conductivity fluctuations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a lot of cases of\Nclean room deterioration lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The construction schedule was\Nshortened by 60 days or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,so some air bubbles\Nmust have gotten mixed in again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The construction in Wing B\Nis awfully slipshod.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That wing was built\Nafter the Angels showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say I'm surprised.\NEverybody is exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Address the issue by tomorrow.\NIkari will raise a stink otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Another water leak?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they say there's corrosion.\NIn the protein wall above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, terrific. Has it affected the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so far, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue, then. We can't abort this test\Nmidway without good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Cdr. Ikari would raise a stink.\N-Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Synchronization position nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Connecting simulation plug to Eva{\i0}\N{\i1}primary body via imitation body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Connection to Eva-00, confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Projecting A.T. Field{\i0}\N{\i1}at strength of 2 yoctos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Contamination alert, Sigma Unit, Floor A!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Protein wall no. 87 has degraded!\NEmitting heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Abnormalities also detected in tube no. 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The corrosion is expanding\Nalong the protein wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like spreading wildfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Abort experiment!\NEmergency seal, tube no. 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixty, 38, and 39 have been sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Corrosion in segment 42 of tube no. 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working! The corrosion is\Nspreading along the walls and lining!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready polysomes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Set lasers to maximum!\NFire at first sign of intrusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Corrosion has reached segment 58\Nof tube no. 6! Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei's imitation body is moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The corrosion is spreading even further!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's attacking the imitation body's\Npituitary system!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rei's status?\N-Unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency eject all plugs!\NHave those lasers ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-An A.T. Field?!\N-That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What... the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Analysis pattern, blue.\NNo doubt about it... it's an Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,An Angel?!\NYou let an Angel infiltrate HQ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, sir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me the excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Physically isolate Central Dogma!\NQuarantine it from the Sigma Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Physically isolating Central Dogma.{\i0}\N{\i1}Sigma Unit will be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're abandoning the Box!\NAll personnel, evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isolating Sigma Unit from Floor D.{\i0}\N{\i1}All bulkheads closing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All personnel within{\i0}\N{\i1}affected areas must evacuate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm aware. I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn off that alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Disabling alarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a false alarm.\NDue to a faulty sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what you will tell\Nthe government and Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Polluted area spreading downwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's spreading out from the Pribnow Box\Nto the entirety of the Sigma Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's a dangerous spot.\N-Yes, it's too close to Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Contain the spread\Nto within the Sigma Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If need be,\Nsacrifice the Geo-front to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Evas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing by at Cage Seven. We can launch\Nonce the pilots are retrieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother waiting for the pilots.\NLaunch them to the surface immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 has top priority. Sacrifice\Nthe other two units to do so if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But, sir, without the Evas,\Nwe can't physically destroy that Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Evas are contaminated\Nbefore then, all is lost. Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All areas of the Central Dogma{\i0}\N{\i1}below the Sigma Unit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will be completely locked down{\i0}\N{\i1}in 60 seconds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the Angel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my work is on hold for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Central Dogma now completely locked down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deep underground facility{\i0}\N{\i1}has been overrun by the intruder.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then, how do we attack\Nthis Angel without any Evas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there's the heavy water boundary.\NThat's a high-oxygen area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a definite preference.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The area where ozone is pumped in\Nto maintain aseptic conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is free of contamination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's vulnerable to oxygen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now pumping in ozone.\NConcentration is increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero-A and Zero-B appear to be recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tube area has returned to normal values.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That core area is pretty resilient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, increase ozone levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's spreading...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is weird. Heat release is increasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Contaminated area is spreading again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The ozone has lost all effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's now steadily ingesting the ozone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt ozone flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's evolving before our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Subcomputer is being hacked into!\NIntruder identity unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! Using Mode C as a countermeasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lowering firewall!\NDeploying decoy interface.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Decoy interface circumvented!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Eighteen seconds to trace!\N-Firewall up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Firewall has been penetrated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploying another decoy interface!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No human could do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Trace successful!\NIt's coming from inside this facility!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Origin, beneath B Wing...\NIt's the Pribnow Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Optical pattern is changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The glowing lines are electrical circuits.\NThis thing is a literal computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploying decoy interface.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Failed! Attempt prevented!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Physically sever the main cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Negative! Not responding to command!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot it with the lasers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's generating an A.T. Field!\NIneffective!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's accessing Security's main banks.\NNow brute-forcing the password.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelfth digit... Sixteenth digit...\ND-word discovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Security Department's main banks\Nhave been compromised!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's accessing the main bank!\NI can't cancel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it after?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's searching through the main path...\NWait, that's the code for... Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's trying to crack the Magi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Crash the I/O system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on your mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Three! Two! One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Power won't shut down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel intrusion continuing!\NIt's accessed Melchior!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop it!\NIt's being taken over by the Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Melchior has been\Nreprogrammed by the Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Artificial intelligence Melchior has{\i0}\N{\i1}proposed autonomous self-destruct.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rejected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rejected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Melchior is now proceeding\Nto hack into Balthasar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, it's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Its computational speed is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Change logic mode!\NSet synch code to 15-second intervals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How much time did that buy us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from its prior speed,\Nabout two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that the Magi\Nhave turned against us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We speculate that this Angel is composed\Nof nano-machines the size of microbes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,These gathered to form a colony\Nand rapidly evolved to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,where it formed AI circuitry\Nin a very short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Evolution?\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They are constantly evolving themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to work out the ideal system\Nto cope with any given situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect example of the system\Nthat life employs to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The only effective method against a target
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that corrects its weaknesses\Nand constantly evolves
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is mutual destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only choice is\Na Magi-Angel double suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I propose the physical elimination\Nof the Magi system.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Unthinkable. Scuttling the Magi\Nis tantamount to sacrificing HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I formally request it\Nas Chief of Operations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Request denied. This is a job\Nfor the Technology Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so stubborn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was my negligence\Nthat caused this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been this way\Nas long as I've known you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Always shouldering the burden by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You never ask for help, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Angel is continuously evolving,\Nit means we have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Encourage its evolution, you mean?\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate end of evolution\Nis self-destruction. Death itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So the solution is to\Naccelerate its evolution?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Angel decides it is the most\Nefficient way to avoid death,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,then it may opt for\Ncoexistence with the Magi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If the target is the computer itself,\Nwe connect Casper directly to the Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:16:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can then reverse-hack it and plant\Na self-destruct acceleration program.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It would also mean lowering\Nits firewall against the Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Casper faster, or is the Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-It will be a race.\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume you'll have\Nthe program ready in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if Casper is also turned,\Nit's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep my promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alarm Code R is in effect.{\i0}\N{\i1}Alarm Code R is in effect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An emergency situation{\i0}\N{\i1}has occurred inside Nerv HQ.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All Class D personnel, please evacuate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are all these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Notes left by the developer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's a backdoor code!\NThis is the Magis' backdoor code!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a treasure trove of Magi hacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I cleared to see this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I never thought of that!\NThis is c-as-integer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This will let us knock out that program\Nin no time! Right, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mother.\NWe'll be ready in time for sure now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand me that socket wrench.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This reminds me of our college days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand me that no. 25 keyboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me a little about the Magi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long story.\NAnd not a very interesting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard of\Nthe Personality Transplant OS?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's that system where a person's\Npersonality is transferred into
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:18:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,a seventh-gen organic computer\Nto let it actually think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same technology\Nused for piloting the Evas, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, the Magi were\Nthe first real-world use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The tech was developed... by my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, your {\i1}mother's{\i0} personality\Nwas transplanted into them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In a manner of speaking,\Nwe're looking at my mother's brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you wanted\Nto protect the Magi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.\NI didn't like my mother enough to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a decision made\Nas a scientist, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Balthasar has been taken over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}AIs are voting in favor of{\i0}\N{\i1}autonomous self-destruct.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's started?!\N-{\i1}In event of unanimous decision,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}self-destruct will occur{\i0}\N{\i1}.02 seconds later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Self-destruct area will encompass{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}geoid depth -280, -140, and Floor Zero.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Due to Exception 582 being in effect...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Balthasar is hacking further into Casper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're losing ground!\N-Its speed is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Self-destruct device{\i0}\N{\i1}will activate in 20 seconds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Casper will be taken over in 18 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Self-destruct device{\i0}\N{\i1}will activate in 15 seconds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We have almost\Na whole second to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A second?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not zero or a negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Maya.\N-Ready here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Four seconds. Three seconds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One second. Zero seconds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,REJECTED
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Autonomous self-destruct{\i0}\N{\i1}has been canceled by AIs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-We did it!\N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Furthermore, Exception 582{\i0}\N{\i1}has also been lifted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Magi system returning{\i0}\N{\i1}to normal operating mode.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}R-Alert lifted. R-Alert lifted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All personnel,{\i0}\N{\i1}stand down to condition one...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's been going on out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! We can't leave these\Nstupid things if we're naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody come and help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sigma Unit now open. Magi system{\i0}\N{\i1}will restart in minus zero three.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I {\i1}am{\i0} getting old.\NAll-nighters do a number on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept your word yet again. Great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Misato, I can't ever remember when\Nyour horrid coffee tasted so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The night before she died,\NMother said something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That the Magi were\Nthree facets of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The scientist in her. The mother in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magi are those three sides of her,\Nconstantly vying for control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She deliberately incorporated\Nthe inner conflict we all have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, the three have\Nslightly different programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never be a mother,\Nso I'll never understand that side of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As a scientist, though,\NI had a great deal of respect for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a woman,\Nthere was a part of me that hated her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-You sure are talkative today.\N-It's been known to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Casper was implanted with my mother's\Npersonality traits as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman in her held on\Nto the bitter end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:22:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.26,0:23:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seele, the cabal which secretly controls{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nerv and the Human{\i0}\N{\i1}Instrumentality Project.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are Cdr. Ikari's actions merely{\i0}\N{\i1}the realization of the Dead Sea Scrolls?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode!{\i0}\N{\i1}"Seele, the Seat of the Soul"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tune in next time{\i0}\N{\i1}for lots more fan service!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Translator: Dan Kanemitsu\NSubtitle Editor: David Fleming
